content:
Suppose we have a JSON file that contains a list of cities as shown below:
{
 "cities": [
   {"name": "Pittsburgh", "population": 302407},
   {"name": "Houston", "population": 2296224},
   {"name": "Atlanta", "population": 498715}
 ]
}
Using this data, how can we construct a sentence that includes one of the cities without mentioning the entire list explicitly?
